唔係唯一嘅道德基礎 佢只係一種觀點或者睇法 將佢哋視為金科玉律或者ultimate solution都係一個不智嘅做法"},{"pid":"ccc282242ac33afad13e0ba8bc14ad34ea4a5cea","tid":881058,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T20:29:03.000Z","msg":"因為係神既安排黎!<br />\n基督教係因信得救<br />\n天主教就要睇行為<br />\n死之後depending on behaviour, 會去地獄/煉獄/天堂"},{"pid":"1c5b7d2e9c906ac7dc95ccc424f10c229ce6ad48","tid":881058,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccc282242ac33afad13e0ba8bc14ad34ea4a5cea","tid":881058,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T20:29:03.000Z","msg":"因為係神既安排黎!<br />\n基督教係因信得救<br />\n天主教就要睇行為<br />\n死之後depending on behaviour, 會去地獄/煉獄/天堂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T22:11:30.000Z","msg":"做咗壞事搵神父懺悔就唔會去煉獄了"},{"pid":"e83a5cff4b70741dbefc1a6bb8904789dce1741e","tid":881058,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"佢地係卧底黎"},{"pid":"afd0f1a15553c2dfddf9360355c7b67f1621f062","tid":881058,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T04:12:20.000Z","msg":"其實我想表達既係希望教會可以拒絕黑社會而唔係咩神大愛全部人，特別當佢重犯錯3，4次之後"}]}